name: Multiplayer Challenge: Boss Deck - Final Fantasy VII
cleanName: Multiplayer Challenge Boss Deck Final Fantasy VII
extDescription:
Multiplayer Challenge Boss Deck - Final Fantasy VII includes:
• 70 Boss Fight-specific cards*
• 30 reprinted cards**
• Reprinted Legendary cards and Starter cards, 3 cards each
• Kadaj [11-140S] Premium Full Art Card
• Rufus [8-109L] Standard Card

name: Kadaj EX (Full Art)
extDescription:
EX BURST When Kadaj enters the field, select 1 of the 3 following actions. "Choose 1 Forward. Dull it." "Choose up to 2 cards from either player's Break Zone. Remove them from the game." "Choose 1 Forward. Until the end of your turn, it gains +2000 power and Brave."
At the end of each of your turns, you may remove Kadaj from the game. If you do so, at the end of your opponent's turn, play Kadaj onto the field.

name: Sephiroth (B-028)
extDescription:
Brave
When Sephiroth attacks, dull all the Forwards opponent controls. At the end of each of your turns, remove all the cards in your opponent's Break Zone from the game.

name: President Shinra
extDescription:
President Shinra cannot leave the field due to your opponent's Summons or abilities. You can play 2 or more Dark Characters onto the field.
If President Shinra is on the field, President Shinra can produce CP of any Element.
2T: Draw 1 card.

name: Hojo
extDescription:
Hojo cannot leave the field due to your opponent's Summons or abilities.
If Hojo is on the field, Hojo can produce CP of any Element.
t: Play 1 Card Name Sephiroth from your hand onto the field.

name: Weiss
extDescription:
When Weiss enters the field, you may play 1 Character from your hand onto the field.
When Weiss attacks, all the Forwards you control gain +2000 power until the end of the turn.

name: Shelke
extDescription: When Shelke enters the field, you may play 1 Forward from your hand onto the field. If you do so, your opponent discards 1 card.

name: Genesis Avatar
extDescription:
Genesis Avatar is also Card Name Genesis in all situations.
When Genesis Avatar enters the field, deal 9000 damage to all the Forwards opponent controls.

name: Scarlet
extDescription:
T: Select up to 3 of the 3 following actions.
"Choose up to 2 Characters. Dull them."
"Choose 1 Character. Freeze it."
"Your opponent discards 1 card."

name: Angeal Penance
extDescription:
Angeal Penance is also Card Name Angeal in all situations.
Haste
When Angeal Penance deals damage to your opponent, break all the Forwards opponent controls.

name: Shinra Soldier
extDescription: When Shinra Soldier enters the field, you may search for up to 2 Card Name Shinra Soldier and add them to your hand. Then, you may play any number of Card Name Shinra Soldier from your hand onto the field.

name: Tseng
extDescription:
The Forwards other than Tseng you control gain +2000 power.
When Tseng enters the field, you may search for 1 Job Member of the Turks and play it onto the field.

name: Sephiroth (B-038)
extDescription:
First Strike
When Sephiroth enters the field, choose 1 Forward and 1 Backup. Break them.

name: Sephiroth EX (B-039)
extDescription:
EX BURST When Sephiroth enters the field, choose 1 Character. Break it.
Octaslash S: Choose up to 1 Forward, up to 1 Backup, and up to 1 Monster. Remove them from the game.

name: Heidegger
extDescription:
When Heidegger enters the field, choose up to 2 Forwards. Break them.
LT, put Heidegger into the Break Zone: Reveal the top 5 cards of your deck. Add 1 Forward among them to your hand and return the other cards to the bottom of your deck in any order.

name: Reeve EX
extDescription: EX BURST When Reeve enters the field, choose 1 Forward of cost 3 or less in your Break Zone. Play it onto the field.

name: Bahamut
extDescription: Deal 10000 damage to all the Forwards opponent controls.

name: Shiva EX
extDescription: EX BURST Choose up to 3 dull Forwards. Break them. Your opponent discards 1 card.

name: Alexander
extDescription: Choose 1 Character of cost 4 or more. Break it.

name: Carbuncle EX
extDescription: EX BURST All the Forwards you control gain +5000 power until the end of the turn. Draw 1 card.

name: Ramuh
extDescription:
Select up to 2 of the 4 following actions.
"Choose 1 Monster. Break it."
"Choose 1 Forward of cost 4 or less. Break it."
"Choose 1 active Forward. Deal it 8000 damage."
"Choose 1 Forward. It gains Haste until the end of the turn."

name: Leviathan
extDescription:
Select 1 of the 3 following actions.
"Choose up to 3 Forwards. Return them to their owners' hands."
"Choose 1 action ability. Cancel its effect."
"During this turn, if a Forward you control is dealt damage by a Summon or an ability, the damage becomes 0 instead."

name: Rufus EX
extDescription:
EX BURST When Rufus enters the field, you may search for 1 Job Member of the Turks and play it onto the field.
When Rufus or a Job Member of the Turks you control is put from the field into the Break Zone, choose 1 Forward opponent controls. Deal it 10000 damage.

name: Rude
extDescription: If you control a Job Member of the Turks other than Rude, Rude gains First Strike.

name: Reno
extDescription: If you control a Job Member of the Turks other than Reno, Reno gains Haste.

name: Elena
extDescription:
Haste
Elena cannot be blocked.
If you control a Job Member of the Turks other than Elena, Elena cannot be chosen by your opponent's Summons.

name: Cissnei
extDescription:
When Cissnei enters the field, you may discard 1 card. When you do so, choose 1 Forward. Deal it 9000 damage.
Damage 3 -- Cissnei gains Haste and Brave.

name: Shalua
extDescription:
The Card Name Shelke you control gains +5000 power.
T, put Shalua into the Break Zone: Choose 1 Forward. During this turn, the next damage dealt to it becomes 0 instead.

name: Restrictor EX
extDescription: EX BURST When Restrictor enters the field, you may search for 1 Job Tsviets and play it onto the field.
